title: Fernhill E2/C2 — feeding Smoke (authored trait) and gaining a shadow
story: fernhill
description: The authored `feedable` trait with its keyed data field
  (`feedable with food the kipper`): feeding refuses without the food and
  after the account is settled; the kipper (via the full tool chain)
  settles it, the follower tags along, and her fed-state nose hint fires
  once in the greenhouse.
